---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="이동수하우스 | 생활·환경 IT 솔루션"
            description="공공데이터·하이브리드 IT로 생활과 환경을 개선합니다.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative text-center py-20">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold leading-tight tracking-tight">
      생활과 환경을 바꾸는 <span class="gradient-text">공공데이터 기반 IT</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-5 text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
      온라인과 오프라인을 연결하는 실용 솔루션으로, 일상 속 문제를 빠르게 해결합니다.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-8 flex items-center justify-center gap-3">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">문의하기</a>
      <a href="/services" class="btn btn-ghost">서비스 보기</a>
    </div>

    <!-- 장식용 라디얼 빛 (부드러운 떠다니는 효과) -->
    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-0 -bottom-10 mx-auto w-[560px] h-[560px] rounded-full blob floaty
                bg-[radial-gradient(circle,_rgba(10,42,107,0.35),_transparent_60%)]"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- Features -->
  <section aria-labelledby="features" class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-10">
    <h2 id="features" class="sr-only">주요 특징</h2>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <span class="inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg
                      bg-[radial-gradient(circle,_rgba(71,163,255,0.2),_transparent_60%)]
                      text-[--color-primary]">
          <!-- 아이콘 -->
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor">
            <path d="M3 6h18M3 12h18M3 18h18" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>
        </span>
        <h3 class="font-semibold">공공데이터 활용</h3>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
        대기질·교통·날씨·부동산 등 데이터를 실제 서비스로 연결.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <span class="inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg
                      bg-[radial-gradient(circle,_rgba(110,231,255,0.2),_transparent_60%)]
                      text-[--color-primary]">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor">
            <path d="M12 3l8 6v12H4V9l8-6z" stroke-width="2" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </span>
        <h3 class="font-semibold">생활·환경 맞춤 코드</h3>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
        스마트홈, 에너지 모니터링, 예약 등 실사용 중심의 개발.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <span class="inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg
                      bg-[radial-gradient(circle,_rgba(71,163,255,0.2),_transparent_60%)]
                      text-[--color-primary]">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor">
            <circle cx="8" cy="12" r="3" stroke-width="2"/><circle cx="16" cy="12" r="3" stroke-width="2"/>
            <path d="M11 12h2" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>
        </span>
        <h3 class="font-semibold">IT+오프라인 융합</h3>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
        교회·주민센터·상가 등 현장 운영에 맞춘 하이브리드 솔루션.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
